    "body": "Hello,\r\n\r\nI am not sure if this is a bug or am I doing something wrong here. I have synced about 12 numbers which are my co-workers and I would need to send them a message when there is a new email in our support e-mail.\r\n\r\nHowever, whenever it reaches the 8th message, it automatically get's banned. Is there anything that I am doing wrong here?\r\n\r\nThis is the current flow:\r\n\r\n1. They have added the source number in their contacts and synced with whatsapp.\r\n2. Ran through these 12 numbers through sendSync($contacts)\r\n3. After that, when a new email comes in, it will run through a loop to notify these 12 co-workers but it hits the not-authorized message when it tries to send the 9th time.",
    "closed_at": null,
